{"tid":2411390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"＜大英＞ 英國外交部：香港不再為「國際金融中心」，是「國際商業樞紐」","createTime":"2021-02-17T09:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T12:50:27.000Z","uid":227801,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"642be8f8087a52c2f537dcf5fee877239ba12b7c","tid":2411390,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T09:49:50.000Z","msg":"最早對金融出手嘅國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-hub-02172021041257.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fhtm%2Fhk-hub-02172021041257.html&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN2%2FS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=b84f409c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-hub-02172021041257.html</a><br />\n香港國際金融中心地位被除名？英外交部 : 香港是國際商業樞紐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國外交部發表最新營商指引，在第二段重點提到港版國安法已削弱了香港基本人權和自由，國安法已滲入學術、校園、圖書館，教科書中涉及政治元素的內容因此被移除。而警察亦利用國安法拘捕示威者與及傳媒擁有者。在港區國安法下，香港可能出現寒蟬效應與及自我審查。&nbsp;<br />\n在2月16日更新的營商指引中，還在有關香港經濟段落中刪去香港是國際金融中心的描述，改稱為具高競爭力的國際商業樞紐（highly competitive global business hub）。&nbsp;<br />\n新的指引同時提到，有表面證據顯示，有私營企業員工的政見原因，甚至參與示威，因此遭受中國當局的壓力。"},{"pid":"7f8833f2b00e588387ea40af0d626b46b58db55f","tid":2411390,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T09:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b384ce4e26da4d9c7eefd8d569e6eca7727fd8","tid":2411390,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T09:54:27.000Z","msg":"日出.gif"},{"pid":"f4578433e5444975787a4b9997c6a7993122a713","tid":2411390,"uid":221171,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T09:56:44.000Z","msg":"明明已經有國安法 同 無晒反對黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解個社會仲咁亂？"},{"p